    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Stay warm and comfortable on your outdoor adventures with ASR Outdoor hand warmers. These air-activated warmers are perfect for keeping your hands toasty in cold weather without the need for external power or electricity. With a working temperature range of 124-155°F, these hand warmers provide just the right amount of warmth without getting too hot. They&#039;re also safe, odorless, and non-toxic, so you can use them without any worries. Each hand warmer lasts up to 10 hours, making them ideal for outdoor activities like hiking, camping, skiing, and more. They come in convenient pack sizes of 10, 25, 50, and 100, so you can choose the perfect amount for your needs. To use, simply open the package and expose the warmer to air</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Cold Weather 10 Hour Hand Warmer Pocket Camp Fire Survival Prepper</h2>\n  <p>Stay warm and comfortable on your outdoor adventures with ASR Outdoor hand warmers. These air-activated warmers are perfect for keeping your hands toasty in cold weather without the need for external power or electricity. With a working temperature range of 124-155°F, these hand warmers provide just the right amount of warmth without getting too hot. They&#039;re also safe, odorless, and non-toxic, so you can use them without any worries.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>LONG-LASTING HEAT - Stay warm for up to 10 hours with these hand warmers. Perfect for outdoor activities in cold weather.</li>\n    <li>MAINTAINS A COMFORTABLE TEMPERATURE - These hand warmers keep your hands warm without getting too hot. They maintain a temperature range of 124-155°F, perfect for cold weather and outdoor sports.</li>\n    <li>EASY TO ACTIVATE - Simply expose the warmer to air and it will start to heat up. No need for any external power source or electricity. Convenient and easy to use.</li>\n    <li>SAFE AND ODORLESS - These hand warmers are made of safe, odorless, and non-toxic materials. Use them without worrying about any harmful chemicals or strong smells. Great for all ages.</li>\n    <li>VARIOUS PACK SIZES - Choose from pack sizes of 10, 25, 50, or 100 hand warmers. Perfect for short trips or extended stays, there&#039;s a size for every need.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/Survival/HP122-10H_Hand_Warmer_main10pk_PL.psd-2.jpg\" alt=\"Stay warm and comfortable on your outdoor adventures with ASR Outdoor hand warmers\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASRHW8H</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 181227387874</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> White</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Each hand warmer lasts up to 10 hours, making them ideal for outdoor activities like hiking, camping, skiing, and more. They come in convenient pack sizes of 10, 25, 50, and 100, so you can choose the perfect amount for your needs. To use, simply open the package and expose the warmer to air. The hand warmer will heat up on its own and provide gentle warmth for hours.</p>\n  <p>Don&#039;t let the cold weather keep you from enjoying your favorite outdoor activities. Stay warm and comfortable with ASR Outdoor hand warmers.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
